SUMMARY:YOGA IN NATURE™ at Apex Nature Park
DESCRIPTION:Yoga In Nature™\, NC\nJoin us for a 60 minute slow vinyasa f
 low to yin yoga practice\, designed for beginners (to intermediate) AND fi
 rst timers WELCOME.\nThe yoga practice (breath and asana) is infused with 
 a connection to nature in order to help calm the mind and energize the bod
 y.\nYoga heals.\nNature heals.\nCost is $15/person payable by cash\nOR Ven
 mo @Darlene-Genander (0862 if asked)\nOR PayPal dgenander@yogainnature.com
 \nAlso accepting payment with Zelle\nBring your yoga mat\, water\, towel o
 r plastic liner for under your mat (if you want to protect it from ground/
 wet) or anything else you may use for your yoga practice.\nWEAR LAYERS\nHo
 pe to see you soon!
